New module: core/whale_profiler.py
- WhaleProfile dataclass with behavioral metrics, CategoryStats, strategy classification
- WhaleProfiler fetches leaderboards (overall + per-category), open/closed positions
- Strategy classification: CONVICTION, SPECIALIST, DIVERSIFIED, MARKET_MAKER, UNKNOWN
- Category-specific credibility scores (PnL, win rate, sample size)
- signal_weight() method: key output consumed by ensemble estimator
- Persistent storage to data/whale_profiles.json (accumulates across runs)

Updated: core/probability.py
- New profiled_whale_estimator() — uses profile data, discounts market makers
- New create_profiled_ensemble() factory
- Backward compatible fallback to PnL-based weighting

Updated: core/context_enricher.py
- WhaleEnricher accepts optional profiler, attaches profile data to positions
- EnrichedContext.to_prompt_section() shows strategy types, signal weights
- LLM prompt includes whale profile interpretation guidance
- ContextEnricher accepts whale_profiler parameter

Updated: strategies/enriched_edge_detector.py
- use_whale_profiles flag, loads profiler, swaps in profiled estimator

Updated: run_pipeline.py
- --profile-whales, --whale-report, --whale-profiles modes

Also: added .gitignore, cleaned up __pycache__
